name: SideChefRecipes
0: ”Alexa, ask Side Chef to show me pasta recipes”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: side chef
Developer Terms of Use
des: With the SideChef skill, select from a vast collection of recipes developed by professional chefs and fan-favorite food bloggers to find one that best fits your craving. Our easy-to-follow video and photos recipes, specifically adapted for Amazon Alexa, will guide you through each step from start to finish.
